public interface DynNetwork<T>

DynNetwork is an the interface to the object that represents a dynamic network composed of CyNodes, connecting CyEdges, attributes, and the respective time intervals DynIntervals. It provides the link to the current static CyNewtork. In addition it maintains the information about dynamic attributes DynAttribute in form of a DynIntervalTree.
